{"title":"劳动者的塑像——题哈尔滨松花江防洪纪念塔","authors":["杨川庆"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":7,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动者的塑像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——题哈尔滨松花江防洪纪念塔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨川庆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从岁月，从充满梦幻的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隆起。如光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迸射千缕辉煌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站起来就是英雄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔座上，垒满了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动者自强的信仰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往事是风，飘过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪水淹没过苦难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也创造过苦难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一次浪涌，拍打呜咽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也发出呜咽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颤栗这个城市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下创伤和回忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史应该永远记住那个日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受难者变成主人了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也就有了主人的自豪和勇敢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当远处涌来一片迷濛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们挺起主人的胸膛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"完成了这个主人的雕像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑望东去江水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谛听中央大街涌动的喧响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站立着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以英雄安泰的英姿"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}